# Visitor Counter

A serverless website that tracks and displays live visitor counts.

## Architecture
S3 → CloudFront → API Gateway → Lambda → DynamoDB

## AWS Services Used
- S3 — static website hosting
- CloudFront — CDN and HTTPS
- API Gateway — REST endpoint
- Lambda — serverless backend
- DynamoDB — counter storage

